   Air Monitoring Station

   What is Airnet?

   Airnet is a radiological ambient air sampling network in Los Alamos,
   Santa Fe, and Rio Arriba counties designed to measure levels of
   airborne radionuclides (plutonium, tritium, and uranium) that may be
   emitted from Laboratory operation.

